Enum VeinTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<VeinTool>
      • wtf.choco.veinminer.api.VeinTool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<VeinTool>
    public enum VeinTool
extends Enum<VeinTool>
    Tools recognised by VeinMiner and it's code. Tools are limited to those listed in the enumeration.
